column3: Pop in on visit to homepro centre
column4: Three of us had lunch here two portions of fried rice. Fried pork and pork noodle soup. Three cokes. Service good and prompt. Place very clean. Portions were good. Food was good especially the soup. Bill 400 baht. Recommended for a visit.
